<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Mon, 29 Jan 2024 12:12:05 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>想离开加沙吗？支付我们 10,000 美元</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-01-29/ty-article-magazine/.premium/want-out-of-gaza-pay-us-10-000/0000018d-54ee-df5c-a1ad-54ff690e0000</link><description>在加沙，在流离失所的加沙人试图躲避以色列的炸弹的影响下，进入埃及的拉法口岸的贿赂业正在蓬勃发展。埃及否认这一点，但一名埃及研究人员表示，“开罗最高官员”参与其中</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Jan 2024 11:46:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-01-29/ty-article-magazine/.premium/want-out-of-gaza-pay-us-10-000/0000018d-54ee-df5c-a1ad-54ff690e0000</guid></item><item><title>巴勒斯坦诉拜登：“我的家人被我的钱杀害了。”新闻。拜登可以结束这一切”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-01-29/ty-article/.premium/my-family-is-being-killed-on-my-dime-pres-biden-could-put-an-end-to-this/0000018d-54b3-df5c-a1ad-54f7a03e0000</link><description></description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Jan 2024 10:28:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-01-29/ty-article/.premium/my-family-is-being-killed-on-my-dime-pres-biden-could-put-an-end-to-this/0000018d-54b3-df5c-a1ad-54f7a03e0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列议会听取因支持国际法院案件而驱逐左翼 MK 的论点</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-29/ty-article/.premium/israels-knesset-hears-arguments-for-expulsion-of-left-wing-mk-over-support-for-icj-case/0000018d-54a5-d0fc-a9bd-5efd2da80000</link><description>去年 12 月，奥弗·卡西夫在国际法院签署支持南非种族灭绝指控的请愿书后，70 名议员提出罢免他</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Jan 2024 10:09:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-29/ty-article/.premium/israels-knesset-hears-arguments-for-expulsion-of-left-wing-mk-over-support-for-icj-case/0000018d-54a5-d0fc-a9bd-5efd2da80000</guid></item><item><title>以色列教育部长：重新安置加沙的呼吁“超级合法”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-29/ty-article/israels-education-minister-calls-to-resettle-gaza-are-super-legitimate/0000018d-543f-dfdc-a5ad-de7f0e290000</link><description>约阿夫·基什部长对支持耶路撒冷定居点会议的分裂性的唯一批评是其时机。部长甘茨所在政党的成员表示，这一事件“分裂了以色列社会并增加了对政府的不信任”</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Jan 2024 09:18:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-29/ty-article/israels-education-minister-calls-to-resettle-gaza-are-super-legitimate/0000018d-543f-dfdc-a5ad-de7f0e290000</guid></item><item><title>以色列士兵在海法被碾压重伤，袭击者下车后用斧头开枪射击</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-29/ty-article-live/netanyahu-gaps-remain-as-talks-on-new-hostage-deal-with-hamas-progress-in-paris-summit/0000018d-52f1-d7e4-a7ad-5af7a2c00006</link><description>一名士兵在海法袭击中受重伤 ■ 两名士兵在以色列北部被真主党火箭弹击中轻伤 ■ 奥地利、罗马尼亚等国家因涉嫌参与哈马斯屠杀而暂停对近东救济工程处的资助 ■ 以色列国防军：数十名恐怖分子在加沙中部和北部的袭击中丧生 ■无人机袭击约旦基地，造成 3 名美国士兵死亡、25 人受伤，拜登誓言做出回应 ■ 胡塞武装向亚丁湾的美国军舰发射火箭</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Jan 2024 03:58:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-29/ty-article-live/netanyahu-gaps-remain-as-talks-on-new-hostage-deal-with-hamas-progress-in-paris-summit/0000018d-52f1-d7e4-a7ad-5af7a2c00006</guid></item><item><title>以色列表示巴黎峰会后对哈马斯人质协议进展的估计仍然存在巨大差距</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-28/ty-article/.premium/amid-estimates-of-progress-on-hostage-deal-israel-says-wide-gaps-persist-after-summit/0000018d-51e3-d5c3-a9fd-75ff0c670000</link><description>一位消息人士告诉国土报，“如果以色列和哈马斯成功弥合关键差距，协议可能会在几天或几周内完成。”据报道，主要争议在于停火期限，但一名以色列官员称与卡塔尔和美国官员的会面是“积极的”</description><pubDate>Sun, 28 Jan 2024 21:34:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-28/ty-article/.premium/amid-estimates-of-progress-on-hostage-deal-israel-says-wide-gaps-persist-after-summit/0000018d-51e3-d5c3-a9fd-75ff0c670000</guid></item><item><title>以哈马斯袭击造成的创伤为由，以色列大学考试中的大屠杀章节将被放弃</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-28/ty-article/.premium/citing-trauma-of-hamas-attack-holocaust-chapter-in-israeli-matric-exam-to-be-waived/0000018d-51ba-d12b-afcd-d1fe2ac90000</link><description>10 月 7 日之后，教育工作者在讲述犹太人在大屠杀期间的经历时面临着情感和心理上的困难，以色列教育部长表示尚未做出最终决定</description><pubDate>Sun, 28 Jan 2024 21:19:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-28/ty-article/.premium/citing-trauma-of-hamas-attack-holocaust-chapter-in-israeli-matric-exam-to-be-waived/0000018d-51ba-d12b-afcd-d1fe2ac90000</guid></item><item><title>斯莫特里奇推迟以色列 2024 年预算，以期纳入联盟资金并避免审查</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-28/ty-article/.premium/smotrich-delays-2024-budget-in-a-bid-to-include-coalition-funding-and-avoid-review/0000018d-5189-dfdc-a5ad-dbffc8fb0000</link><description>据信，斯莫特里奇试图避免审查，并将联盟资金“隐藏”在更大的预算中。如果预算在2月19日之前未获得批准，则需要全面削减700亿谢克尔</description><pubDate>Sun, 28 Jan 2024 21:17:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-28/ty-article/.premium/smotrich-delays-2024-budget-in-a-bid-to-include-coalition-funding-and-avoid-review/0000018d-5189-dfdc-a5ad-dbffc8fb0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列总统谴责国际法院对其言论的描述，称加沙有无辜的巴勒斯坦人</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-28/ty-article/herzog-blasts-icjs-portrayal-of-his-remarks-says-there-are-innocent-palestinians-in-gaza/0000018d-51cb-dfdc-a5ad-dbffce970000</link><description>国际法院的报告指出，赫尔佐格在 10 月 12 日的新闻发布会上谈到加沙的巴勒斯坦人时表示，“整个国家”应对这场大屠杀负责。周日，他说，“我对他们歪曲我的话的方式感到厌恶”，指责他们“支持捏造的法律争论”</description><pubDate>Sun, 28 Jan 2024 21:12:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-28/ty-article/herzog-blasts-icjs-portrayal-of-his-remarks-says-there-are-innocent-palestinians-in-gaza/0000018d-51cb-dfdc-a5ad-dbffce970000</guid></item><item><title>谁真正决定拜登的以色列-加沙政策？从内圈向外，重要美国官员指南</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-01-28/ty-article-magazine/.premium/mapping-the-biden-administration-on-israel-gaza-and-the-palestinians/0000018d-4f4b-d02c-a79f-4fdb83090000</link><description>10月7日之前，美国和以色列优先考虑以色列与沙特关系正常化。现在，拜登政府正试图释放哈马斯扣押的人质，阻止与真主党的战争，并在加沙的战争和人道主义灾难中打击以色列的外交地位。以下是负责处理一系列日益加剧的担忧的美国官员</description><pubDate>Sun, 28 Jan 2024 20:13:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-01-28/ty-article-magazine/.premium/mapping-the-biden-administration-on-israel-gaza-and-the-palestinians/0000018d-4f4b-d02c-a79f-4fdb83090000</guid></item><item><title>国家将向在加沙战斗中丧生的菲律宾裔以色列国防军士兵的父母授予公民身份</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-28/ty-article/.premium/state-to-grant-citizenship-to-parents-of-filipino-israeli-soldier-killed-in-gaza-fighting/0000018d-5189-d5c3-a9fd-75ddded40000</link><description>西德里克·加林 (Cydrick Garin) 和其他 20 名士兵在加沙的一座建筑倒塌中丧生。他的父母是来自菲律宾的民工，他的父亲在他出生后就被驱逐出境。他的母亲说：“他是菲律宾公民，但他将一生奉献给了他深爱的祖国以色列”</description><pubDate>Sun, 28 Jan 2024 20:05:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-28/ty-article/.premium/state-to-grant-citizenship-to-parents-of-filipino-israeli-soldier-killed-in-gaza-fighting/0000018d-5189-d5c3-a9fd-75ddded40000</guid></item><item><title>欧盟主席错误地暗示奥斯威辛集中营是波兰而非德国，引发波兰抗议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-28/ty-article/eu-chief-erroneously-suggests-auschwitz-was-polish-not-german-sparking-protest-in-poland/0000018d-511e-d3ab-a5cf-539f2b7d0000</link><description>欧盟委员会主席乌苏拉·冯德莱恩随后发表帖子澄清奥斯威辛是纳粹德国的灭绝营。近年来，波兰严厉打击了公众对其在大屠杀中所扮演角色的批评</description><pubDate>Sun, 28 Jan 2024 19:59:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-28/ty-article/eu-chief-erroneously-suggests-auschwitz-was-polish-not-german-sparking-protest-in-poland/0000018d-511e-d3ab-a5cf-539f2b7d0000</guid></item><item><title>近东救济工程处充斥着哈马斯。但以色列别无选择</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-28/ty-article/.premium/unrwa-is-riddled-with-hamas-but-israel-has-no-alternative/0000018d-5122-d3ab-a5cf-53bf4b370000</link><description>在近东救济工程处难民机构的一些成员参与了 10 月 7 日的大屠杀后，西方国家政府可能已经冻结了向近东救济工程处难民机构支付的款项。然而，像以色列一样，他们知道帮助加沙地带的巴勒斯坦人至关重要</description><pubDate>Sun, 28 Jan 2024 19:37:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-28/ty-article/.premium/unrwa-is-riddled-with-hamas-but-israel-has-no-alternative/0000018d-5122-d3ab-a5cf-53bf4b370000</guid></item><item><title>巴勒斯坦歌手参加当地比赛后，冰岛成为早期欧洲歌唱大赛的热门人选</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-28/ty-article/.premium/iceland-becomes-early-eurovision-favorite-after-palestinian-singer-enters-local-contest/0000018d-50ec-d3f3-a5ff-53fd5e840000</link><description>巴沙尔·穆拉德 (Bashar Murad) 将于五月与其他九首冰岛歌曲竞争，代表北欧国家参赛。与此同时，卢森堡选择以色列裔卢森堡人塔利·戈勒甘特(Tali Golergant)作为其官方代表</description><pubDate>Sun, 28 Jan 2024 18:01:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-28/ty-article/.premium/iceland-becomes-early-eurovision-favorite-after-palestinian-singer-enters-local-contest/0000018d-50ec-d3f3-a5ff-53fd5e840000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡部长与数千名以色列人一起参加“重新安置加沙”会议，呼吁转移巴勒斯坦人</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-28/ty-article/ministers-from-netanyahus-party-join-thousands-of-israelis-at-resettle-gaza-conference/0000018d-512f-dfdc-a5ad-db7f35e10000</link><description>以色列极右翼国家安全部长表示，“我们需要找到一种合法的方式让[巴勒斯坦人]自愿移民”。随后，利库德集团的一名议员解释说，在战争中，“自愿是你强加给[某人]的一种状态，直到他们同意为止。” &amp;#39;;以色列反对派领导人抨击会议：“它破坏了潜在的协议并危及以色列国防军士兵”</description><pubDate>Sun, 28 Jan 2024 17:55:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-28/ty-article/ministers-from-netanyahus-party-join-thousands-of-israelis-at-resettle-gaza-conference/0000018d-512f-dfdc-a5ad-db7f35e10000</guid></item><item><title>近东救济工程处表示，在调查完成之前不会处理 10 月 7 日针对员工的指控</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/2024-01-28/ty-article/.premium/unrwa-says-it-will-not-address-employees-oct-7-allegations-prior-to-probes-completion/0000018d-507e-d12b-afcd-d0feef570000</link><description>巴勒斯坦总统阿巴斯办公室猛烈抨击九个国家停止向近东救济工程处提供资金的决定，称以色列针对近东救济工程处的行动是为了“消除巴勒斯坦难民问题”；近东救济工程处发言人表示，只能在下个月之前在加沙提供服务</description><pubDate>Sun, 28 Jan 2024 16:30:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/2024-01-28/ty-article/.premium/unrwa-says-it-will-not-address-employees-oct-7-allegations-prior-to-probes-completion/0000018d-507e-d12b-afcd-d0feef570000</guid></item><item><title>在强烈反对下，数百名学者集会支持领导哈佛大学反犹太主义工作组的犹太研究学者</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-01-28/ty-article/.premium/academics-rally-behind-jewish-studies-scholar-heading-harvards-antisemitism-task-force/0000018d-5086-d3f3-a5ff-53d739d20000</link><description>超过 300 名研究犹太历史、以色列社会、反犹太主义和大屠杀的学者表示，德里克·彭斯拉教授 (Derek Penslar) 是担任美国大学新工作组联合主席的理想人选，并认为针对他的反犹太主义指控是荒谬的。</description><pubDate>Sun, 28 Jan 2024 15:52:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-01-28/ty-article/.premium/academics-rally-behind-jewish-studies-scholar-heading-harvards-antisemitism-task-force/0000018d-5086-d3f3-a5ff-53d739d20000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队阻止抗议者阻止人道主义援助进入加沙地带</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-28/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-prevents-protesters-from-blocking-humanitarian-aid-entry-into-gaza-strip/0000018d-5073-dfdc-a5ad-da7f10990000</link><description>一名抗议者说，“战争时期你不能援助敌人，加沙人也是敌人的一部分。”以色列国防军部署了路障，并宣布穿越边境为军事禁区，以阻止右翼抗议者阻挡救援卡车进入</description><pubDate>Sun, 28 Jan 2024 15:31:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-28/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-prevents-protesters-from-blocking-humanitarian-aid-entry-into-gaza-strip/0000018d-5073-dfdc-a5ad-da7f10990000</guid></item><item><title>伊朗向太空发射三颗卫星，标志着随着中东紧张局势加剧，其能力有所增强</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-01-28/ty-article/iran-launches-three-satellites-into-space-showing-increased-capabilities-as-tensions-rise/0000018d-508d-dfdc-a5ad-daff4c490000</link><description>伊朗崭露头角的太空计划受到了西方的批评，一些人表示，在以色列-加沙战争和代理人势力的参与导致局势日益不稳定的情况下，这“缩短了伊朗伊斯兰共和国开发洲际弹道导弹的时间表”</description><pubDate>Sun, 28 Jan 2024 15:23:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-01-28/ty-article/iran-launches-three-satellites-into-space-showing-increased-capabilities-as-tensions-rise/0000018d-508d-dfdc-a5ad-daff4c490000</guid></item><item><title>报告：加沙地带 80% 的隧道网络仍然完好无损</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-28/ty-article/report-80-percent-of-gaza-strips-tunnel-network-still-intact/0000018d-4fab-d35c-a39f-effbcb0a0000</link><description>据《华尔街日报》报道，以色列仅摧毁了哈马斯在加沙的隧道基础设施的 20% 至 40%，由于对人质福利的担忧，以色列的行动进展缓慢</description><pubDate>Sun, 28 Jan 2024 12:43:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-28/ty-article/report-80-percent-of-gaza-strips-tunnel-network-still-intact/0000018d-4fab-d35c-a39f-effbcb0a0000</guid></item></channel></rss>